---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy | HEIC to JPG Converter — browserpixels"
	description="Our HEIC to JPG converter is 100% client-side. We do not collect, store, or upload your images. Read the full privacy policy for the free, private HEIC to JPG converter."
	canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
	<main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-14 transition-colors duration-300 sm:py-20">
		<header class="mb-10">
			<div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 px-3.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-emerald-700 transition-colors duration-300 dark:border-emerald-900 dark:bg-emerald-950 dark:text-emerald-300 w-fit">
				<span class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" />
				Your privacy is the whole point
			</div>
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">
				Privacy Policy
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-500 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-slate-400 sm:text-base">
				Last updated: July 12, 2026
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="space-y-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-slate-300 sm:text-base">
			{/* The headline clause — what reviewers look for */}
			<div class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-5 text-neutral-800 transition-colors duration-300 dark:border-emerald-900 dark:bg-emerald-950/60 dark:text-emerald-100 sm:p-6">
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					The short version
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-2">
					This tool is 100% client-side. We do not collect, store, or upload any of your images or personal data. All image processing happens locally in your web browser.
				</p>
			</div>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					1. How your images are handled
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					When you load a HEIC or WebP file into our converter, that file is read directly into your browser's memory and decoded on your own device using JavaScript and WebAssembly. Nothing about your image is ever transmitted to our servers, because there are no servers — the entire conversion takes place in your browser. When you leave or refresh the page, the data is gone from memory.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3">
					We do not upload, cache, log, or retain any file you convert, and we have no access to the contents of your images.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					2. Personal data
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					We do not ask you to register, sign in, or provide any personal information to use the converter. We do not collect names, email addresses, or device identifiers through the tool itself.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-3">
					If you contact us directly (for example, by email), we will use your message solely to respond to your inquiry and will not add you to any marketing list.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					3. Cookies
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					We only use essential cookies and analytics:
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
					<li>
						<strong class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Essential cookies.</strong> A single preference cookie stores your light/dark theme choice so the site remembers it next time. This is set locally and contains no identifying information.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Analytics.</strong> If enabled, analytics helps us understand aggregate, anonymized traffic (e.g. page views) so we can improve the tool. We do not use analytics to track individual users across other sites.
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3">
					We do not use cookies to display personalized advertising based on your browsing behavior, other than through the third-party services described below.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					4. Third-party services
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					To keep this tool free, we display ads through <strong class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Google AdSense</strong>. AdSense and its partners may use cookies and device identifiers to serve ads and measure their performance. Below is Google's official notice for users in the European Economic Area, and the choices available to you.
				</p>
				<ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5">
					<li>
						Google may use cookies (including the DoubleClick cookie) to serve ads based on your prior visits to this and other websites.
					</li>
					<li>
						You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a class="font-medium text-emerald-700 underline decoration-emerald-300 underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-300 hover:decoration-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400 dark:decoration-emerald-700" href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a>.
					</li>
					<li>
						You can learn more about how Google uses data when you use our site from its <a class="font-medium text-emerald-700 underline decoration-emerald-300 underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-300 hover:decoration-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400 dark:decoration-emerald-700" href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">partner-sites policy</a>.
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-3">
					Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on a user's previous visits to this website or other websites. The use of cookies allows them to serve ads based on your interests. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					5. Children's privacy
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					Our service is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us and we will delete it.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					6. Your rights
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					Depending on where you live, you may have the right to access, correct, or delete personal data we hold about you. Because we do not collect personal data through the converter, we have nothing to return or erase on that side. For any direct-message data, just contact us and we will honor your request.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					7. Changes to this policy
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review it periodically.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-300 dark:text-white">
					8. Contact us
				</h2>
				<p class="mt-3">
					If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can reach us at
					<a class="font-medium text-emerald-700 underline decoration-emerald-300 underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-300 hover:decoration-emerald-500 dark:text-emerald-400 dark:decoration-emerald-700" href="mailto:hello@browserpixels.com">hello@browserpixels.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<footer class="pt-6">
				<a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-700 transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 dark:hover:text-emerald-300">
					← Back to the converter
				</a>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
